---
---

<section id="robots" class="robots-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>Three steps. Your voice in, published content out.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="robots-grid">
      <div class="robot-card">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="robot-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>Feed Your Voice</h3>
        <p class="robot-tagline">Weekly Ritual + Personas</p>
        <ul class="robot-features">
          <li>Complete a 5-minute weekly ritual</li>
          <li>Define your audience personas</li>
          <li>AI learns your voice, tone, positioning</li>
          <li>Your narrative arc evolves over time</li>
          <li>Content stays authentically you</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="robot-card featured">
        <div class="featured-badge">The Magic</div>
        <div class="robot-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>AI Generates Content</h3>
        <p class="robot-tagline">Multiple Formats, One Pipeline</p>
        <ul class="robot-features">
          <li>Content angles matched to your audience's problems</li>
          <li>Articles, newsletters, social posts, shorts</li>
          <li>Real keyword data drives every piece</li>
          <li>Affiliate links woven in automatically</li>
          <li>Scheduled at the best time for each platform</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="robot-card">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="robot-icon">👆</div>
        <h3>Swipe & Publish</h3>
        <p class="robot-tagline">Review in Seconds</p>
        <ul class="robot-features">
          <li>Open the app on your phone</li>
          <li>Swipe right to publish, left to skip</li>
          <li>Edit inline if needed</li>
          <li>Published to all connected channels</li>
          <li>Track performance in analytics</li>
          <li>If publishing backend is offline, actions are queued and retried automatically</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .robots-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-white) 0%, var(--color-light-gray) 100%);
  }

  .robots-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .robot-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .robot-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .robot-card.featured {
    border: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .step-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: 20px;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    right: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .robot-icon {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .robot-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .robot-tagline {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .robot-features {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .robot-features li {
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-light-gray);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .robot-features li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .robot-features li::before {
    content: "\2192  ";
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .robot-card.featured {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }
</style>
